’Ł@9f1a690075920b95ec8368ac75f2d116a726091b421b91d6930b507e5a05ba19ŁŠTitle: title: attr category
Path: Examples
Content:
Add a category to a custom command.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> # Double numbers
    @category math
    def double []: [number -> number] { $in * 2 }


```
